00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.114
So one has to understand that today's message

00:00:14.234 --> 00:00:19.682
is that we inculcate purity.

00:00:19.802 --> 00:00:24.120
We should not cheat ourselves. It is easy to cheat

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:27.815
but we should inculcate purity

00:00:27.935 --> 00:00:34.952
within ourselves as a matter of our own maturity,

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:40.120
as our own decoration, as our own beauty

00:00:40.240 --> 00:00:46.156
and not just because it's a laborious thing

00:00:46.276 --> 00:00:50.364
or it is a very hard thing, not like that.

00:00:51.165 --> 00:00:55.240
It should be achieved with great pleasure and happiness.

00:00:55.360 --> 00:00:59.004
How do we like to have a bath or to be clean

00:00:59.124 --> 00:01:01.320
and to be presentable?

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:06.360
In the same way we should try to clean our thoughts.

00:01:06.480 --> 00:01:09.560
Just by paying attention to them, we can clean them.

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:11.240
Thoughts must be made clean.

00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:15.160
First of all why have thoughts at all.

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:20.080
But even if you have, have clean and pure thoughts.

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:23.400
Even if you have to have, don't have thoughts

00:01:23.520 --> 00:01:27.880
full of arrogance, aggression or of fear.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.426
Some people think that if you have thoughts of fear

00:01:30.466 --> 00:01:34.120
it's a very good thing: "Oh I'm frightened, I am afraid."

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:38.440
It's impurity. Why should you be afraid?

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:41.040
That means your left Vishuddhi is catching.

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:44.920
There's no need to have any fear of any kind;

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:47.607
no need to have any fear of any kind.

00:01:47.727 --> 00:01:53.160
If you have to have fear that means there's something wrong.

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:56.080
If you believe that God is above all,

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:58.080
you are a realized soul and that

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:01.920
God is going to look after you,

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:04.000
that He is your father,

00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:06.440
that He's open His gates to you,

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:08.600
what is there to be afraid of?

00:02:08.720 --> 00:02:12.080
Many people think that way that if you have the fears,

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:15.676
you are humble. Humility is different

00:02:15.796 --> 00:02:17.960
from a frightened person.

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:22.400
It's absolutely a [INAUDIBLE] it has nothing to do with humility.

00:02:22.520 --> 00:02:26.480
So to be humble is different

00:02:26.868 --> 00:02:29.440
and to be frightened is different.

00:02:29.560 --> 00:02:34.080
For Sahaja Yogis it is very easy to find out

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:36.960
through their vibratory awareness

00:02:37.080 --> 00:02:41.160
what is fear and what is humility.

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:43.360
As humility will give you vibrations

00:02:43.480 --> 00:02:48.560
and fear will catch all your left side.

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:57.360
So our purification of our mind comes

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:01.560
through certain methods of understanding ourselves.

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:06.120
First of the understandings one has to have

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:22.960
is that we are born in a family, born in a society,

00:03:23.080 --> 00:03:26.360
born in a so-called religious sect or what.

00:03:27.720 --> 00:03:29.560
So all these fixations

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:35.520
have put into us certain amount of impurities.

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:41.153
Which may give us ego, superego, anything it might give us.

00:03:41.273 --> 00:03:46.273
So to keep it pure and simple is:

00:03:46.942 --> 00:03:50.696
take to water element as much as you can.

00:03:50.816 --> 00:03:54.804
It helps both ways, it helps ego, it helps superego.

00:03:54.924 --> 00:03:56.480
Take to water element.

00:03:56.600 --> 00:03:59.480
And that is what Lakshmi is.

00:03:59.600 --> 00:04:06.960
Lakshmi is the one that gives you the Mahalakshmi Tattwa.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:11.120
From the Lakshmi only the Mahalakshmi's principle comes in.

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:14.080
And this is after the purification

00:04:14.200 --> 00:04:15.840
through the Lakshmi process.

00:04:15.960 --> 00:04:17.120
Christ has said,

00:04:17.240 --> 00:04:22.760
"If you want I can give you gold, gold parts,

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:24.520
you can live with it.

00:04:24.640 --> 00:04:27.280
But those who love Me will only enter

00:04:27.400 --> 00:04:31.400
into the Kingdom of God. And I will eat with them,"

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:33.960
means those who are pure only I will eat with them.

00:04:34.080 --> 00:04:38.640
I will not eat with people, who are impure.

00:04:38.920 --> 00:04:41.520
He was so, I mean, every,

00:04:41.640 --> 00:04:45.720
all the incarnations are aware of it,

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:47.880
that they have to be with the pure people

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.800
and they have to help the pure people.

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:55.000
But He so clearly said it that if you want Lakshmi,

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:59.080
you can have it, that's money.

00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:01.400
But that's not Mahalakshmi,

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:04.720
so from Lakshmi to Mahalakshmi state.

00:05:04.840 --> 00:05:06.440
You've already got your realization,

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:08.840
you do not know how much you have got it already.

00:05:08.960 --> 00:05:12.200
You are already having the Mahalakshmi principle within you.

00:05:12.320 --> 00:05:14.600
And what is the Mahalakshmi principle?

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:20.400
That's the point. Can I ask this question?

00:05:26.440 --> 00:05:30.000
What is the Mahalakshmi principle within you?

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:38.160
Yogi: It's all for the Spirit.

00:05:38.960 --> 00:05:42.200
Shri Mataji: No, no. But you have a power.

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:47.520
You have got MahaLakshmi's powers within you, do you know that?

00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:53.840
Yogi: The pleasure it gives you.

00:05:54.320 --> 00:05:56.440
Shri Mataji: The pleasure? No, no, no.

00:05:56.640 --> 00:05:59.120
Yogi: The power of giving realization.

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:03.080
Shri Mataji: Go ahead still, little more, more.

00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:06.800
Pleasure is not a power.

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:09.200
Pleasure is what you enjoy.

00:06:09.320 --> 00:06:12.200
But you have a power of Mahalakshmi.

00:06:13.320 --> 00:06:18.320
Yogi: Sustaining power.

00:06:18.640 --> 00:06:20.800
Shri Mataji: That's no power.

00:06:20.960 --> 00:06:27.360
Power means, you have that power to do something.

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:34.760
Yogi: The power to spread Sahaja yoga.

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:38.560
Shri Mataji: That's rather vague, particular one.

00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:43.400
Yogi: Power to give realization.

00:06:44.560 --> 00:06:49.760
Yogi: To evolve.

00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:53.320
Shri Mataji: But to evolve is your own.

00:06:53.440 --> 00:06:57.240
Power is what you do to others.

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:01.080
The whole thing I told you just now.

00:07:01.200 --> 00:07:05.000
Is to purify.

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:08.760
You have the power to purify.

00:07:10.080 --> 00:07:12.840
How do you cure people?

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:16.640
By purifying them.

00:07:16.760 --> 00:07:19.360
All right?

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:24.640
Now just think how you purify others,

00:07:24.760 --> 00:07:30.880
by talking to others you can purify them.

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:35.840
By touching others, you can purify them.

00:07:35.960 --> 00:07:39.960
By looking at them, you can purify them.

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:44.040
One person who is a realized soul, purifies the whole atmosphere.

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:46.880
