00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:50.680
Since I've come, it has been warm enough.

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:55.160
You purify everything.

00:07:55.280 --> 00:07:59.840
You purify this light, do you notice that?

00:07:59.960 --> 00:08:03.200
You've awakened the light.

