Now what other powers you have?

00:08:17.400 --> 00:08:19.840
Yogi: To raise the Kundalini.

00:08:19.960 --> 00:08:22.040
Shri Mataji: That's awakening.

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:26.080
See Kundalini is many powers, is many-folded.

00:08:27.604 --> 00:08:32.560
You purify yourselves, others and yourselves.

00:08:32.680 --> 00:08:36.400
Some more powers are there. Now come along, let's have it.

00:08:38.017 --> 00:08:40.360
You all have those powers and you are not aware of them

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:44.680
this is the best part of it.

